<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 18:19:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特别报道：英特尔内部，首席执行官帕特·基辛格（Pat Gelsinger）摸索着美国偶像的复兴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/inside-intel-ceo-pat-gelsinger-fumbled-revival-an-american-icon-2024-10-29/</link><description>英特尔与台湾台积电达成了一项甜蜜的协议，台积电将生产英特尔设计但无法生产的芯片。消息人士称，它还向英特尔提供大幅折扣。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 17:35:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/inside-intel-ceo-pat-gelsinger-fumbled-revival-an-american-icon-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>ASMI 上调人工智能指引，中国需求依然强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmis-third-quarter-bookings-beat-expectations-ups-guidance-2024-10-29/</link><description>芯片制造设备供应商 ASM 国际 (ASMI) 周二预测，由于人工智能继续推动高端订单，而中国订单降幅小于预期，第三季度预订量超出预期，因此第四季度指引将上调。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 17:23:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmis-third-quarter-bookings-beat-expectations-ups-guidance-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>全球需求疲软，Moncler 第三季度销售额下滑 3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-moncler-slip-3-third-quarter-global-demand-weakens-2024-10-29/</link><description>按固定汇率计算，意大利奢侈外套制造商 Moncler 第三季度收入下降 3%，略高于分析师预期，其所有主要市场均表现疲软。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 16:50:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-moncler-slip-3-third-quarter-global-demand-weakens-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税，可能会遭到北京方面的强烈反对</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-slaps-tariffs-chinese-evs-risking-beijing-payback-2024-10-29/</link><description>在其最引人注目的调查结束后，欧盟决定将中国制造的电动汽车的关税提高至高达 45.3%，该调查导致欧洲分裂并引发北京方面的报复。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 16:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-slaps-tariffs-chinese-evs-risking-beijing-payback-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>法国部长就“政治”干邑关税挑战中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-minister-challenge-china-over-political-cognac-duties-2024-10-29/</link><description>两位法国外交消息人士周二表示，当法国贸易部长索菲·普里马斯下周访问上海时，法国将就白兰地进口关税问题向中国发起挑战，巴黎方面称此举具有政治性且不合理。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 14:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-minister-challenge-china-over-political-cognac-duties-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲汽车安全机构冷落比亚迪Atto 3驾驶员辅助系统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-car-safety-agency-snubs-byds-atto-3-driver-assistance-system-2024-10-29/</link><description>欧洲汽车安全机构对比亚迪Atto 3 EV所使用的驾驶员辅助系统发布了“不推荐”评级，这对这家正在努力在欧洲大陆扩张的中国汽车制造商造成了打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 13:43:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-car-safety-agency-snubs-byds-atto-3-driver-assistance-system-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>阿菲夫重夺亚足联年度最佳球员，塞克获得女子奖项</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/afif-reclaims-afc-player-year-seike-takes-womens-award-2024-10-29/</link><description>周二，在首尔举行的亚洲足球联合会年度颁奖典礼上，卡塔尔球员阿克拉姆·阿菲夫第二次被评为亚洲足球联合会年度最佳球员，来自日本的 Kiko Seike 获得了女子冠军。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 13:02:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/afif-reclaims-afc-player-year-seike-takes-womens-award-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车中国老板将电动汽车折扣视为“业务的一部分”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-china-boss-sees-ev-discounts-part-business-2024-10-29/</link><description>德国汽车制造商中国区总裁拉尔夫·布兰德斯塔特 (Ralf Brandstaetter) 周二在接受商报采访时表示，大众汽车将中国电动汽车折扣视为“业务的一部分”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 12:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-china-boss-sees-ev-discounts-part-business-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员敦促彻底改革海关计划以阻止芬太尼化学品走私</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-senators-urge-overhaul-customs-program-stop-fentanyl-chemical-smuggling-2024-10-29/</link><description>在路透社报道揭露毒贩如何利用简化的入境系统将中国制造的芬太尼化学品几乎不受限制地偷运到美国后，美国著名民主党参议员周二呼吁拜登政府打击一项受欢迎的免税海关计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 12:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-senators-urge-overhaul-customs-program-stop-fentanyl-chemical-smuggling-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>芬兰警告习近平朝鲜在乌克兰战争中“挑衅”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/finlands-president-raises-ukraine-war-security-issues-with-chinas-xi-2024-10-29/</link><description>芬兰总统亚历山大·斯塔布表示，他周二在北京会谈期间代表北约和欧盟向中国国家主席习近平表示，朝鲜与俄罗斯的活动是升级和挑衅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 11:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/finlands-president-raises-ukraine-war-security-issues-with-chinas-xi-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>维吾尔人权机构在波斯尼亚举行会议，安全严密，应对威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/uyghur-rights-body-meets-bosnia-under-tight-security-over-threats-2024-10-29/</link><description>报告称，在威胁和压力要求取消后，一个在中国和海外为维吾尔人权利而奋斗的机构不得不在波斯尼亚首都在警方保护下进行几乎秘密的会面。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 11:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/uyghur-rights-body-meets-bosnia-under-tight-security-over-threats-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>法国海军舰艇通过敏感的台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/french-naval-vessel-passes-through-sensitive-taiwan-strait-2024-10-29/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，一艘法国海军舰艇通过台湾海峡，这是西方国家通过战略水道的最新一次任务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 11:11:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/french-naval-vessel-passes-through-sensitive-taiwan-strait-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>小米推出更快版旗舰电动车挑战特斯拉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-chief-touts-nurburgring-record-ahead-ev-launch-2024-10-29/</link><description>小米周二推出了 SU7 电动跑车的豪华版，称这款售价 114,000 美元的车型将成为量产中最快的四门汽车，直接挑战特斯拉和保时捷等公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 10:16:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-chief-touts-nurburgring-record-ahead-ev-launch-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国 iPhone 需求旺盛，苹果公司营收将实现两年来最大增幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-set-biggest-revenue-jump-two-years-iphone-demand-china-2024-10-29/</link><description>苹果公司预计将在周四公布两年来最大的季度收入增幅，在该公司年度发布周期结束时，iPhone 需求的表现将好于近年来，尤其是在中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 10:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-set-biggest-revenue-jump-two-years-iphone-demand-china-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国考虑在未来几年额外举债超过1.4万亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/eyeing-us-election-china-considers-over-14-trillion-extra-debt-over-next-few-2024-10-29/</link><description>支出计划表明，北京已采取更高的刺激措施来提振经济，尽管这仍然不是一些投资者一直呼吁的 2008 年那样的火箭筒。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 08:33:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/eyeing-us-election-china-considers-over-14-trillion-extra-debt-over-next-few-2024-10-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>